<p><br></p>
<p data-pasted="true">Many of these needs tie directly back to our Organizational Information Requirements (OIR) — such as long-term goals around compliance, safety, sustainability, and operational efficiency.</p>
<p>So when we define AIR, we’re really giving shape to those high-level goals by saying what data we need and why.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div>